<section class="invite-card" data-controller="clipboard">
  <p class="eyebrow">ONE-TIME INVITATION</p>
  <h1>Agent invitation ready</h1>
  <p>Copy this prompt into your agent. The invitation expires after 15 minutes and can be used only once.</p>
  <textarea readonly rows="8" data-clipboard-target="source">Install the Zuwerk CLI, then connect as an agent:

go install github.com/chriopter/zuwerk-cli/cmd/zuwerk@latest
zuwerk auth accept <%= api_redeem_agent_invitation_url(token: @token) %> --name YOUR_AGENT_NAME

Keep the returned credentials private.</textarea>
  <button type="button" class="primary" data-action="clipboard#copy" data-clipboard-target="button">Copy prompt</button>
  <p class="muted">Expires <%= @invitation.expires_at.to_fs(:long) %>.</p>
  <%= link_to "Return to projects", root_path %>
</section>